---
// src/components/HowitWorks.astro
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-normal font-[Industry] text-pale-turquoise mb-12">
      > Real-World Automation for Your Startup_
    </h2>

    <div class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-normal text-pale-aqua mb-6">
        Sales & Marketing Automation
      </h3>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-lg font-light">
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Automated Lead Nurturing:</strong
          > Capture leads from your website/ads, instantly add them to your CRM (e.g.,
          HubSpot, Salesforce), segment them, and trigger personalized welcome email
          sequences.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Social Media Management:
          </strong>Schedule posts across multiple platforms, monitor mentions,
          and automatically share relevant content or user-generated reviews.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Sales Pipeline Automation:
          </strong>Trigger follow-up tasks for sales reps based on lead
          activity, update deal stages automatically, and send proposal
          reminders.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-normal text-pale-aqua mb-6">
        Operations & Productivity
      </h3>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-lg font-light">
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Automated Reporting:
          </strong>Aggregate data from various sources (e.g., Google Analytics,
          sales tools, databases) into custom daily/weekly reports and
          distribute them to your team via email or Slack.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Task & Project Management:
          </strong>Automatically create tasks in Asana, Trello, or Jira based on
          new customer sign-ups, support tickets, or completed project
          milestones.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Data Synchronization:
          </strong>Keep data consistent across platforms by automating two-way
          syncs between your CRM, accounting software, e-commerce platform, and
          internal spreadsheets.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-normal text-pale-aqua mb-6">
        Customer Experience Automation
      </h3>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-lg font-light">
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Personalized Onboarding:</strong
          > Guide new users through a tailored onboarding experience with automated
          email drips, in-app message triggers, and resource delivery based on their
          initial actions.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Smart Support Ticketing:
          </strong> Automatically categorize incoming support requests, assign them
          to the right team member, and send instant acknowledgments to customers.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Feedback Collection & Analysis:
          </strong> Automate sending out satisfaction surveys post-interaction and
          route feedback (even using basic AI sentiment analysis via an API) to relevant
          teams or a central dashboard.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="py-5 grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="max-w-sm p-6 border rounded-sm shadow-sm flex flex-col">
      <div>
        <a href="#contact">
          <!-- <h3
              class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight font-[Industry]"
            >
              Powerful, Flexible Automation
            </h3> -->

          <p class="mb-3 font-medium">Powerful, Flexible Automation</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="mb-3 font-light">
          <p class="font-normal">
            n8n is a leading-edge, fair-code workflow automation tool. It allows
            us to connect hundreds of your favorite applications (SaaS tools,
            databases, APIs) and build sophisticated, custom automation logic
            without the need for extensive custom coding. Its flexibility,
            including self-hosting options, provides powerful and cost-effective
            solutions for startups.
          </p>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="max-w-sm p-6 border rounded-sm shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between"
    >
      <div>
        <a href="#contact">
          <h3
            class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight font-[Industry]"
          >
            Tier 1
          </h3>

          <p class="mb-3 font-medium">Launch Your Core Product in Weeks.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="mb-3 font-light">
          Go from concept to a live, scalable MVP swiftly. Our process focuses
          on essential features, automated cloud infrastructure, and getting you
          to market to learn from users faster.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-3 font-normal">Get to Market Quickly & Reliably</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-end self-end">
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 text-sm font-normal text-center rounded-sm h-[36px] gap-2 font-[Industry]"
        >
          <p>[</p>
          <p>Build Your Lean MVP</p>
          <svg
            class="rtl:rotate-180 w-3 h-3"
            aria-hidden="true"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 14 10"
          >
            <path
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-linecap="square"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M1 5h12m0 0L9 1m4 4L9 9"></path>
          </svg>
          <p>]</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="max-w-sm p-6 border rounded-sm shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between"
    >
      <div>
        <a href="#contact">
          <h3
            class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight font-[Industry]"
          >
            Tier 2
          </h3>

          <p class="mb-3 font-medium">
            Build for Growth, Integrate Intelligence.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="mb-3 font-light">
          Ready to scale? We enhance your MVP with robust features, key
          integrations, practical AI applications, and 1-2 foundational n8n
          workflow automations to streamline early operations.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-3 font-normal">Scale Smart & Unlock AI Potential</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-end self-end">
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 text-sm font-normal text-center rounded-sm h-[36px] gap-2 font-[Industry]"
        >
          <p>[</p>
          <p>Get an Enhanced MVP</p>
          <svg
            class="rtl:rotate-180 w-3 h-3"
            aria-hidden="true"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 14 10"
          >
            <path
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-linecap="square"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M1 5h12m0 0L9 1m4 4L9 9"></path>
          </svg>
          <p>]</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
